Install needed packages (on a Debian-based system):
apt-get install git make
apt-get install --no-install-recommends asciidoc

Generating git docbook documentation:
- Clone git
- apply patch
- change (system/global) asciidoc.conf
  - comment:
    lsquo=&#8216;
    rsquo=&#8217;
    ldquo=&#8220;
    rdquo=&#8221;
    (^-- )=&#8212;&#8201;
    (\n-- )|( -- )|( --\n)=&#8201;&#8212;&#8201;
    (\w)--(\w)=\1&#8212;\2
    (\w)'(\w)=\1&#8217;\2
- make xml
- take *.xml files

